{{vgname2|用Wii玩|ja=Wiiであそぶセレクション|en=New Play Control!|cn=用Wii玩|tw=以Wii遊玩}}是任天堂为[[Wii|Wii]]再开发的一系列[[任天堂GameCube|任天堂GameCube]]游戏。用Wii游玩系列中的游戏做了若干强化，最知名的是用[[Wii遥控器|Wii遥控器]]与[[Nunchuk|双截棍]]实现操作<ref name="controls">{{cite web|url=http://uk.wii.ign.com/articles/915/915529p1.html|title=First Look: Wii de Asobu Pikmin|author=John Tanaka|date=2008-10-02|accessdate=2008-10-05|publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]|archive-date=2011-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110625030725/http://uk.wii.ign.com/articles/915/915529p1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，此外还有宽屏支持和强化图形<ref name="present">{{cite web|url=http://uk.wii.ign.com/articles/915/915548p2.html|title=Presenting the "Play it on Wii Selection"|author=Lucas M. Thomas|date=2008-10-02|accessdate=2008-10-08|publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]|archive-date=2009-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090123044203/http://uk.wii.ign.com/articles/915/915548p2.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

